---
import Layout from '../layouts/PageWithTitle.astro';
import { GITHUB_REPO } from '../consts';
---

<Layout
	title="The Company"
>
	<p>
		Fieldwork was inspired by our shared frustrations with developing firmware. We felt that coding agents 
		do not perform as well at low-level embedded work as they do at the more common application/web/scripting work.
	</p>
	p>
		The reason for this is simple - these tasks are under-represented in training data. Our aim here is to fill in that gap.
	</p>
	<div class="section-title">
		<h1>The People</h1>
		<hr />
	</div>
	<div class="people-grid">
		<article class="person-card">
			<figure>
				<div class="headshot-placeholder" role="img" aria-label="Headshot placeholder for Person 1"></div>
				<figcaption>Tim Krasnoperov, Co-Founder / CEO</figcaption>
			</figure>
			<p>Tim leads the company and focuses on the development of benchmark tasks </p>
			<p class="profile-link">LinkedIn: Placeholder</p>
		</article>
		<article class="person-card">
			<figure>
				<div class="headshot-placeholder" role="img" aria-label="Headshot placeholder for Person 2"></div>
				<figcaption>August O'Beirne, Co-Founder</figcaption>
			</figure>
			<p>August also contributes to benchmark tasks, performs PM duties, and builds </p>
			<p class="profile-link">
				LinkedIn:
				<a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/august-obeirne/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
					https://www.linkedin.com/in/august-obeirne/
				</a>
			</p>
		</article>
		<article class="person-card">
			<figure>
				<div class="headshot-placeholder" role="img" aria-label="Headshot placeholder for Person 3"></div>
				<figcaption>Conlon Meek, Co-Founder</figcaption>
			</figure>
			<p>Conlon is the electronics SME at Fieldwork, responsible for assmebling the apparatus that allows for
			development of the benchmark and environment on real hardware. Conlon is a MechE from UC Berkeley and an
			experienced hardware engineer having worked </p>
			<p class="profile-link">LinkedIn: Placeholder</p>
		</article>
		<article class="person-card">
			<figure>
				<div class="headshot-placeholder" role="img" aria-label="Headshot placeholder for Person 4"></div>
				<figcaption>Matt McCoolgan, Co-Founder</figcaption>
			</figure>
			<p>Matt brings the hardware and software sides of this project together, primarily being responsible for
			building cloud systems that access microcontroller hardware. Matt comes from ???</p>
			<p class="profile-link">LinkedIn: Placeholder</p>
		</article>
	</div>
</Layout>

<style>
	:global(.prose) {
		width: 920px;
		max-width: calc(100% - 2em);
	}

	:global(.prose p),
	:global(.prose li),
	:global(.prose figcaption) {
		font-size: 0.95rem;
	}

	.section-title {
		margin-bottom: 1em;
		padding: 1em 0;
		text-align: center;
		line-height: 1;
	}

	.section-title h1 {
		margin: 0 0 0.5em 0;
	}

	.people-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
		gap: 1.5rem;
		margin-top: 1rem;
	}

	.person-card {
		padding: 1rem;
		border: 1px solid #d9d9d9;
		border-radius: 0.75rem;
	}

	.person-card figure {
		margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
	}

	.headshot-placeholder {
		aspect-ratio: 1 / 1;
		width: 100%;
		border-radius: 0.75rem;
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, #efefef, #d9d9d9);
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
	}

	.person-card figcaption {
		font-weight: 600;
	}

	.person-card p {
		margin: 0;
	}

	.profile-link {
		margin-top: 0.75rem;
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.people-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}
	}
</style>
